      • initialize

        protected java.util.Properties initialize()
                                   throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Description copied from class: CredentialGenerator
        Initialize the credential generator. This is provided separately from the CredentialGenerator.init() method for convenience of implementations so that they do not need to store in CredentialGenerator.systemProperties. The latter is convenient for the users who do not need to store these properties rather can obtain it later by invoking CredentialGenerator.getSystemProperties()

        Required to be implemented by concrete classes that implement this abstract class.

        Specified by:
        initialize in class CredentialGenerator
        Returns:
        A set of extra properties that should be added to Gemfire system properties when not null.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when there is a problem during initialization
